These exclusions match the CRL-0 boundary posture
(docs/licenses/CRL-0.md) and the OEL-1 evaluation posture
(docs/licenses/OEL-1.md).

Each paper on Zenodo is its own canonical citable artifact and carries
its own license metadata as set on its Zenodo record.
